What a sudden uplifting news from Forest Watch Indonesia. Tbh I Submitted my short film, "Breathe" awhile back out of curiosity, and it turns out, I got a really wonderful Christmas gift this year. 
It is really a big step for my journey. So many lesson learned during the process and I believe somehow universe will find a way to pay your hardwork and sacrifices. 
I can't make it this far without the love of my life, @christinejohana and all the actors and actress involved. Not to forget God, my parents, my brothers, my best buddies, and of course Forest Watch Indonesia for the opportunity. 
Now I'm ready for what 2017 has to offer.
